<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CertiFried Announcer - Multi-Platform Stream Notifications</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard-style.css?v=2.0.0">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<main class="page-container">
    <div class="page-header">
        <img src="/images/CertiFried.png" alt="Bot Logo" style="width: 128px; height: 128px; border-radius: 50%;" class="mb-3">
        <h1>CertiFried Announcer</h1>
        <p class="lead">The only multi-platform stream announcement bot you'll ever need. Reliable, fast, and fully customizable.</p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mt-4">
            <a href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<%= client_id ;%>&permissions=8&scope=bot%20applications.commands" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" target="_blank">Invite to Server</a>
            <a href="/src/dashboardoard" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Open Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Core Features</h2>
        <div class="row g-4 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-satellite-dish me-2 text-primary"></i>Multi-Platform</h3>
                <p>Notifications for Twitch, YouTube, Kick, Trovo, and TikTok.</p></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-paint-brush me-2 text-primary"></i>Highly Customizable</h3>
                <p>Custom messages, avatars, and names per-streamer or per-channel.</p></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-desktop me-2 text-primary"></i>Web Dashboard</h3>
                <p>Manage everything from a simple and intuitive web dashboard.</p></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-file-csv me-2 text-primary"></i>Bulk Management</h3>
                <p>Use CSV files and mass commands to manage hundreds of streamers easily.</p></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-user-tag me-2 text-primary"></i>Live Role</h3>
                <p>Automatically assign a "Live" role to linked Discord users when they go live.</p></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><h3><i class="fas fa-bolt me-2 text-primary"></i>Reliable & Fast</h3>
                <p>Built with efficiency in mind to deliver announcements as quickly as possible.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>